dataset_id: CAMEX-4 ANDROS ISLAND RAWINSONDE AND RADIOSONDES V1
organizations: Global Hydrology Resource Center, Marshall Space Flight Center, NASA
title: CAMEX-4 ANDROS ISLAND RAWINSONDE AND RADIOSONDES V1
summary: The CAMEX-4 Andros Lisland Rawinsonde and Radiosondes dataset was collected by using numerous rawinsondes (radiosondes), which were launched from Andros Island in support of CAMEX-4. These sondes provided atmospheric soundings of temperature, pressure, relative humidity, wind, and altitude.
